{"tid":1582272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實抗爭係未已經完左？","createTime":"2019-09-20T03:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T07:15:45.000Z","uid":17209,"like":75,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"020a757edfd22d559557b8764dcbdfefe8d35477","tid":1582272,"uid":17209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:34:28.000Z","msg":"呢幾日上連登發現行動post已經唔見晒，全部都係新聞post同制裁post，全部都係轉載緊人地點睇，人地做左啲咩，敵人做左啲咩。咁香港人，示威者做左啲咩？<br />\n<br />\n抗爭要成功唔係要被動地等人犯錯，唔係要等其他人可憐，而係要主動宣傳自己嘅主張，指出敵人嘅錯誤，說服其他人同國家去幫助我地。<br />\n<br />\n我認我好廢，廢到什至如果冇人自發去搞遊行集會，冇任何抗爭運動嘅話，我真係會乜尻都唔做。<br />\n<br />\n但我真係想香港贏。"},{"pid":"477bf9d56f64415caf500f4e4d5f15f4c71df652","tid":1582272,"uid":180819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tCvq3UC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtCvq3UC.jpg&h=4ef224c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JO1NxNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJO1NxNY.jpg&h=eed860ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eaKz1i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eaKz1i.jpg&h=8ff6438b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇完關注行動post啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"90ba23082ff4b130111c242923aae570611d869a","tid":1582272,"uid":211034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"一齊去Twitter將 #929globalantichinazimarch <br />\n推上熱門 推到929全世界所有人都一齊standwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjKZ7PA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjKZ7PA.jpg&h=9c9f7bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5sn1BHW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5sn1BHW.jpg&h=f59429dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stjbYWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai